# Pier della Vigna — an artfully crafted intellect

![essence of Pier della Vigna](pier-della-vigna.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit portrait): pier-della-vigna.tiff -->

**what —** A suicide, now a thorn-tree in the wood of the self-violent, fed on by Harpies.

**why —** Despair drove him to take the life that was not his alone to take.

**how —** He can speak only when a branch is snapped and the wound of him bleeds and hisses.

**where —** Circle VII — Violence against the self.

